data.description: Absolutely Stunning home located on canal access to Cross Lake on private lot with amazing deck off the back. Home has been completely remodeled throughout with New Paint, features, windows, flooring, lighting, and more. Primary suite has large walk-in closet with bath suite with huge luxury shower. Two additional great size bedrooms. Kitchen is fabulous with all updated appliances and built-in grill for those Steak Nights.. Be Ready to Call this your Next HOME.
